
Rivet
=====

* rivet is a mini PHP framework intended to speed development.
* you can route 


Features
--------

* [Twig](http://github.com/fabpot/Twig) templates. Django templates in PHP. Pimp.


Requirements
------------

* PHP 5.2.4ish

Example (index.php)
-------

<?php

	// Include Rivet
	require_once(dirname(__FILE__).'/rivet/Rivet.php');

	// Set some custom config options
	Config::set('template_cache', dirname(__FILE__).'/cache');
	Config::set('template_path', dirname(__FILE__).'/templates/');

	// Site handler
	class Site extends Rivet
	{
		public function __construct()
		{
			$this->route('^/$', 'home', $name='home');
			parent::__construct();
		}

		public function home()
		{
			return new Template('home.html');
		}
	}

	// Create and dispatch the site
	$site = new Site();
	$site->dispatch();
